# Design System UI

- All visual values through semantic tokens — no arbitrary colors, spacing, or font sizes.
- WCAG 2.1 AA: contrast, keyboard, focus-visible, `prefers-reduced-motion`, 44px touch targets.
- shadcn/ui: install on demand, customize to tokens, preserve accessibility primitives.
- Avoid generic AI aesthetics (gratuitous gradients, identical card grids, decorative glow).
- Responsive 320px–2560px. No Framer Motion unless CSS cannot achieve the effect.

Standards: `.cursor/skills/design-system-standards/`. Human docs: `docs/design-system/`.
